overview: When Jerry the dog and his pal Mandy the cat and the always opinionated Frank the parrot are left home alone they do what all pets do: they turn on their TV and watch Funny Dogs, a compilation of some of the funniest dog videos on earth! Join our three furry and feathered friends as they debate which dog is the funniest, the wackiest, the cutest and the most hilarious! FUNNY DOGS 2 is a bark-tastic movie for any dog lover!
title: Funny Dogs 2
